Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 49% niqan 358 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 51% niqan 373 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Amis39%, Bunun7%, Tayal1%, ni rahuq na o2%.
